"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"一些想法：\\n\\n 1/ 胖协议适应于所有细分赛道，包括GameFi，NFTs，Web3等 \\n\\n2/ 长期来看，通用型公链ETH/SOL/AVAX/DOT/NEAR等应取得更大机会，相较专用公链FLOW/IMX等 \\n\\n3/ 专用公链短期要靠NFTs/GameFi/Web3等非金融领域快速吸引新用户，未来才可能在牌桌上占据一席之地 [$IMX](https://twitter.com/search?q=%24IMX&src=cashtag_click)/Ronin/Efinity\\n\\n4/ 押注单游戏爆发的机会小于押注游戏平台。长期来看游戏平台Gala/ [$Mbox](https://twitter.com/search?q=%24Mbox&src=cashtag_click)/ [$PYR](https://twitter.com/search?q=%24PYR&src=cashtag_click) 等应取得更大机会 \\n\\n5/ GamFi内部在迅速分化，粗暴打金类高收益率将成绝响，APY下降不可逆，会到DeFi二池长期收益率100%以内 \\n\\n6/ 如同交易/借贷需求一样，让娱乐需求成为刚需并为之买单/氪金是每一个游戏脱颖而出的必备之路\",\"timestamp\":1639973374,\"title\":\"匹马：一些想法（投资方向）\"},\"digest\":\"CjYA_kVoRIPP2V0Kur6JjLPUwGeDsF1YXdN4JJxh4Wk\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x37D1758e6DE28c28A490e60D9959C470991d93AD\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"chTayNeEfGH_WlFL8gUz1WlLczhPKnfhpfHriGVw7Ec\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"zuDjBEjAn6bczveRlivsQbLX7ggx4ndMih37I_wOfnk\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"dSd6xdD_wpDhklzIRu_oLLSetmnp2kn1ZzpVaH1DdB5BYzyHGgLZHU8ptmRYGP8m1Lufx0pmtWQ-faD0PtndHg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x3028b3c5b834b5ae2cdc1bda3b5b8a205f574bb01b33ef2a609b04240f2bff801bbd47fd7497e6ec74102a2928d8b25fa2bba9bf946d2c83e54f4c2a97e463e41c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"chTayNeEfGH_WlFL8gUz1WlLczhPKnfhpfHriGVw7Ec\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"zuDjBEjAn6bczveRlivsQbLX7ggx4ndMih37I_wOfnk\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"CjYA_kVoRIPP2V0Kur6JjLPUwGeDsF1YXdN4JJxh4Wk\"}"